ISLAMABAD, Oct 12 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar on Saturday held a telephone call with Foreign Minister of Kingdom of Saudi Arabia Prince Faisal bin Farhan Al Saud.
“They discussed the situation in Palestine and Lebanon and expressed their deep commitment and support for the people of Palestine and Lebanon,” a post on X said.
